snippet.title: Ace Combat 5: The Unsung War - TGS 2003 Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The teaser trailer for Ace Combat 5: The Unsung War, shown at Tokyo Game Show 2003.

This trailer was included on the Project Aces Trailer Collection, a DVD collection of interviews for Ace Combat Zero and trailers for Ace Combat 04, 5, and Zero. All rights to this video belong to Bandai Namco Entertainment; it has been uploaded here for archival and encyclopedic purposes. Optional English captions are available.
